{
  "stem": "21482.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he and my mother were getting ready to, to leave to-- with a transport.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, at the last minute, one of the Germans that he knew arranged for him to get a permit.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were talking about leaving.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was going to stay with my-- some other aunt and uncle and my cousins in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was-- I mean, every, every second of your life, your life was in danger.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you didn't know when you went to work in the morning if you will come back at night.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Or if you were, were home at night, if somebody would not knock at your door, and the Gestapo or the soldiers would come in and take you.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You never knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had-- we had no idea.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think anybody knew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We all-- we were told in the beginning that all those people are going to be sent to the farm, that they will help work in, in-- on farms and work in the fields to help grow  food for the army-- for the German Army.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And people believed it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I remember some people who were taken away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then a few weeks later, they would get a, a telegram that their loved one died.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And also, I remember in the beginning, people-- some people would actually get ashes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They say, these are the remains of your father, or brother, or mother, or sister.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "At the very beginning-- after that, that stopped.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "After a while, it stopped.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I think the rumors were slowly started in 1940.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I also think it took us a while before anybody would believe it.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
